## CONTENT STRUCTURE

**H1:** Mob Wife Nails: Bold Glamorous Almond Designs That Command Attention

**H2 Structure:**

1. **What Are Mob Wife Nails and Why Are They Still Dominating in 2026?**
   — Cultural anchoring section. Carmela Soprano, Karen Hill from Goodfellas, Adriana La Cerva. TikToker Kayla Trivieri coining "clean girl is out, mob wife era is in." Google Year in Search 2024: #1 trending aesthetic. Why it has staying power — it is a wardrobe disposition, not a microtrend. Sets the tone for the whole post.

2. **The Mob Wife Nail Colour Palette: Deep Reds, Burgundy, Black, and Gold That Mean Business**
   — Core colour territory. Classic red as the power anchor. Sultry burgundy, dramatic black, metallic gold and silver, chocolate oxblood. What each shade communicates. Almond nails introduced here as the shape that carries these colours best — the elongated tip deepens their impact.

3. **What Nail Shape Does the Mob Wife Aesthetic Actually Need? Why Almond Is the Modern Answer**
   — Shape breakdown. Square (OG Carmela, Adriana La Cerva — the classic TV reference). Coffin (dramatic, modern, popular on TikTok). Stiletto (sharpest power statement). Almond (modern editorial evolution — all the power of the look, more versatile, less costume). Why almond is the recommended shape for mirelleinspo.com's audience: elongates, softens where needed, wears the embellishments and colours cleanly.

4. **Bold Mob Wife Nail Designs to Bookmark Right Now: Rhinestones, Chrome, and Glossy Drama**
   — Core design gallery section. Rhinestone coffin / almond sets. Gold chrome finish. High-gloss red. Matte-and-gloss contrast (matte black with gloss gold accents). Foil transfer. Gem-studded accent nails. The principle: strategic embellishment, not scattered clutter.

5. **The Mob Wife French Manicure: Deep French Tips and the Thick White That Started It All**
   — Deep French / thick French as the OG mob wife manicure. London manicurist Mariana Augusto quote: it is "the ultimate mob wife manicure — Britney Spears, Pamela Anderson, Missy Elliott era." Zendaya's 2024 mob wife gel tip manicure at Wimbledon. Modern mob wife French tip variations: zebra-print tip, gold-lined French, oversized square white, almond deep French.

6. **Leopard Print, Crocodile, and Animal Print Mob Wife Nails That Walk Into Every Room First**
   — Animal print as core mob wife design territory. Leopard as the signature print. Cheetah, zebra, crocodile. How to execute on almond nails without looking cheap (colour restraint: keep to brown/black/gold tones rather than neon interpretations). Accent nail vs. full set approach.

7. **Can Mob Wife Nails Work for the Office? The Polished Maximalist Approach**
   — Direct answer: yes, if done right. The "boardroom mob wife" version: dark reds, black with one gold accent nail, understated rhinestones at the cuticle line rather than full coverage, deep French on almond. Positions the look as power dressing, not costume. Natural cross-link hook to office-siren-nails for readers who want to go further.

8. **Mob Wife Nails Without Extensions: How to Get the Energy on Medium and Shorter Lengths**
   — Real answer to pain point 4. Press-on sets as a legitimate entry point (press-ons named in TikTok content as a community-approved option). Gel overlay for length without full extensions. What to prioritise when length is limited: invest in colour richness, gloss quality, and one statement embellishment rather than full coverage rhinestones.

9. **How to Keep Mob Wife Nails Looking Expensive, Not Cheap: The Finish Is Everything**
   — Directly addresses pain point 5. Application quality as the separator. Rhinestone placement principle: strategic and deliberate, never scattered. Gloss finish quality over quantity of embellishment. Maintenance cadence (2–3 week fills). Avoiding harsh chemicals and how to extend longevity at home.

10. **Dark Feminine vs. Mob Wife Nails: Same Power, Different Register**
    — Clear editorial distinction. Mob wife = maximalist glamour, loud luxury, unapologetic opulence. Dark feminine = editorial moodiness, shadow romance, mystery over maximalism. Different audience moments (mob wife for a statement night out; dark feminine for an editorial, moody everyday). Natural internal link to dark-feminine-nails for readers who want to explore the quieter version of this energy.

11. **Mob Wife Maximalism vs. Old Money Restraint: Where You Sit on the Spectrum**
    — Contextual bridge section. Positions mob wife within the broader aesthetic universe — the loudest point on the glamour spectrum, with old money at the other end. Validates the reader's preference for maximalism while acknowledging there is a whole continuum. Natural internal link to old-money-nails.

12. **Your Mob Wife Era Starts Here: How to Brief Your Nail Tech for the Perfect Set**
    — Practical closing section that directly solves pain point 2. Exact language to use at the salon. The four-part brief: shape (almond or coffin) + colour (specific shade direction) + finish (high-gloss, chrome, matte accent) + embellishment (rhinestones, foil, animal print — pick one or two, not all). Reference image advice. What to show your tech. Natural hook to aesthetic-nail-ideas as the broader destination for more inspiration.

**Structure Reasoning:** The H2 architecture opens with cultural authority (why this aesthetic matters in 2026, not just what it is), moves through the four core design territories readers are actively searching (colour, shape, art types, French tips, animal print), then directly addresses the two biggest audience anxieties (wearability and quality), provides cross-aesthetic editorial context through strategic internal link sections, and closes with a practical action section that solves the most common stated problem in the community ("I don't know what to ask for"). Every H2 is either a long-tail ranking target, a direct user question mapped from voice search research, or a natural internal link hook.

